表格班次记录表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblBcDetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblBcDetail
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblBcDetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblBcDetail (
Code varchar(20) not null,
Name varchar(20) null,
BeginTime char(5) null,
EndTime char(5) null,
constraint PK_TBLBCDETAIL primary key (Code)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'记录上班的班次',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblBcDetail'
go
